OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FGenerally dry with variable
OL,6,Fcloud but warm, sunny spells
OL,7,Fdeveloping. Thicker cloud and some
OL,8,Frain arriving from the west through
OL,9,Fthe late evening. Turning breezier
OL,10,Flater.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,13,FCloudier on Wednesday with some rain
OL,14,Flikely. Thursday and Friday, mostly
OL,15,Fdry with bright or sunny spells.
OL,16,FTurning very warm, perhaps locally
OL,17,Fhot, and feeling increasingly humid.
OL,18,FThundery showers possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
